---

<section class="border-b border-primary/20 dark:border-black/20">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
    <!-- Main Heading -->
    <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 p-8 lg:p-12 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-primary/20 dark:border-black/20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight mb-4 font-heading">
        Building The Future With Precision And Excellence
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed max-w-md">
        At ULTRACTION, we transform visions into reality through exceptional construction services, delivering quality projects that exceed expectations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional Text Column 1 -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 border-b lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-primary/20 dark:border-black/20">
      <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 opacity-60">Our Mission</h3>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
        To deliver exceptional construction solutions that embody quality, innovation, and sustainability across every project we undertake.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional Text Column 2 -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-12">
      <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 opacity-60">Our Vision</h3>
